messages.message:
@avi thoughts on “Gain insights and understand what’s in your documents using a chat interface”? And it looks like we have room to provide some examples. “Ask a loan agreement what are the penalties of a late payment?”

Not sure the driver to move from document to file. I think professionals think in terms of documents and would consider images of documents, word, xls, pdf to all be documents. Whereas ‘files’ convey less meaning
